WEBVTT

1
01:22:54.130 --> 01:22:55.120 
他是王室血脉
He is of royal blood.

2
01:22:55.260 --> 01:22:57.540 
- 他杀了特查拉 - 那是仪式格斗
-He killed T'Challa! -In ritual combat.

3
01:22:57.720 --> 01:22:59.550 
那真的要紧吗
Does that really matter?

4
01:23:02.220 --> 01:23:05.140 
你是瓦坎达最伟大的战士
You are the greatest warrior Wakanda has.

5
01:23:05.520 --> 01:23:09.310 
帮我推翻他 别让他羽翼丰满起来
Help me overthrow him before he becomes too strong.

6
01:23:09.480 --> 01:23:10.600 
推翻
Overthrow?

7
01:23:11.520 --> 01:23:12.640 
娜吉雅
Nakia!

8
01:23:14.110 --> 01:23:16.850 
我不是个可以自由来去的探子
I'm not a spy who can come and go as they so choose!

9
01:23:18.610 --> 01:23:23.070 
我要忠于王位 不管坐在上面的是谁
I am loyal to that throne, no matter who sits upon it.

10
01:23:23.700 --> 01:23:25.410 
你忠于什么
What are you loyal to?

